    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and I\u2019ve truly loved every mile in it! It's in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and dependability, ready for its next adventure with a new owner. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
