    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl offers a refined driving experience and a proven track record of reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor surface marks consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is exceptionally well-preserved, featuring dual-zone climate control, heated and ventilated power seats, and a high-definition navigation system. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health; it has been strictly maintained at scheduled intervals with a complete service history available for review. Recent updates include a fresh set of premium all-season tires and a new battery. While there is slight wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster and a few small stone chips on the hood, the car remains a standout example of its class. It is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that provides a quiet, comfortable, and confident ride for its next owner.",
      "price": 34900.0,
